Office of Research API

API interface for The Ohio State University research data.

Built for use by the Office of Research.

Utilizing swagger.io specifications and a custom serverside renderer styled loosely around Swagger Editor.

Version 1.0.0
Contact information
  • Chase McManning
  • mcmanning.1@osu.edu
  • http://research.osu.edu

/fom/departments

GET /fom/departments
deprecated

Summary

Returns a collection of all known departments, in either JSON or XML format.

Description

This is a wrapper around USPFOMgetDeptList, with a local JSON cache for quicker retrieval (24 hour). Currently only in use by the FOM vendor software.

Potentially equivalent to the new API: /api/v1/department

Parameters

Name Location Description Required Schema
json query If set, the response will be in 'application/json' format No string

Responses

Code Description Schema
200 successful operation Fom.Departments
A collection of department entries.
{ +
department: array
[ +
A thin representation of a department.
{ +
dnode: string ????
dnode_title: string ????
id: string Unique department ID
title: string Department title
}
]
}

/fom/project/{list}

GET /fom/project/{list}
deprecated

Summary

Returns a collection of projects with the specified Principal Investigators, in either JSON or XML format.

Description

This is a wrapper around USPFOMgetProjByInv, and currently only in use by the FOM vendor software.

Parameters
